==English==

===Pronunciation===
*ĭngk, /ɪŋk/, /INk/

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}} {{uncountable}} and {{countable}}

#a pigment (or dye) based fluid used for writing, printing etc.
#black or dark coloured fluid ejected by squid, octopus etc, as a protective strategy

